## Quick checklist before opening PR

- [ ] Issue exists and is linked
- [ ] Branch name follows `cursor/{issue}-*-bf51`
- [ ] `bash scripts/verify.sh` passed
- [ ] AI-USAGE.md updated
- [ ] ROADMAP updated if phase gate passed
- [ ] PR body has `Closes #N`
- [ ] Upstream repos untouched
